annotationA: Glutamine synthetase 2 cytoplasmic; Glutamate-ammonia ligase activity. It is involved in the biological process described with: glutamate catabolic process; synapse assembly; neurotransmitter receptor metabolic process; glutamine biosynthetic process
annotationB: Delta-1-Pyrroline-5-carboxylate dehydrogenase 1 is a conserved, nuclear-encoded mitochondrial matrix enzyme. It is a member of the aldehyde dehydrogenase superfamily involved in proline degradation
